<section class="program-phases">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="program-phases__title font-display">The Six Phases</h2>
    <div class="program-phases__timeline">

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">01</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Issue Identification</h3>
          <p>Students surface the education policy issues that affect their daily lives&mdash;discipline, access, resources, representation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">02</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Research &amp; Data Collection</h3>
          <p>Participants gather data, conduct interviews, and build the evidence base for their reform proposals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">03</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Policy Brief Writing</h3>
          <p>Students draft professional policy briefs&mdash;real documents with real recommendations for real decision-makers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">04</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Presentation Development</h3>
          <p>Coaching on public speaking, persuasion, and how to hold a room when the stakes are real.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">05</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">School Board Presentation</h3>
          <p>Students present their findings and reform proposals directly to school board members during public comment or scheduled sessions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="program-phase">
        <span class="program-phase__number font-mono">06</span>
        <div class="program-phase__content">
          <h3 class="program-phase__name font-display">Network &amp; Alumni</h3>
          <p>Graduates join the BRIDGE alumni network&mdash;a pipeline of young education policy advocates connected across DFW and beyond.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

